This document has detailed every step taken in the CA HWTS scraping assignment. We covered:

Project Overview:
Understanding the task and its goals.

Repository Structure:
The organization of files (README, requirements, and main script).

Detailed Code Explanation:
Step-by-step walkthrough of logging, data loading, Selenium configuration, scraping logic, error handling, and data output.

Final Output:
The solution outputs a CSV file (hwts_facilities_output.csv) containing the scraped facility data.

